reviewText: You have to love and apreciate Hal Roach and his little gang of rascals. Only 3 episodes but worth the price! I'm an amid watcher of the rascals but I've never seen Dogs of War, a silent short. Interesting to see a very young Farina, I mean he was a baby. Hal Roach must have really loved Farina because even as a baby he still was on the camera more than the others.
